WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.362
Welcome to RestoreAssist.

00:02.362 --> 00:08.220
In this tutorial, I'll walk you through creating your account.

00:08.220 --> 00:16.220
Step 1: Enter your name, email address, and create a secure password with at least 8 characters.

00:16.220 --> 00:19.906
Step 2: Add your business name and ABN.

00:19.906 --> 00:26.898
We verify your ABN automatically against the Australian Business Register.

00:26.898 --> 00:32.850
Step 3: Check your email inbox for a 6-digit verification code.

00:32.850 --> 00:37.764
Enter it within 10 minutes to activate your account.

00:37.764 --> 00:45.764
Step 4: The Setup Wizard guides you through 5 steps — profile, AI hydration, integrations, health check, and activation.

00:45.764 --> 00:47.764
Step 5: Tap Activate.

00:47.764 --> 00:53.244
All 12 health checks pass, and your workspace is now live.

00:53.244 --> 00:55.606
Welcome to RestoreAssist.